[Pied avocet](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pied_avocet) (Recurvirostra
avosetta). Photo by Borilei via Wikimedia Commons, CC BY-SA 4.0.

The winners of the international stage of the “Wiki Loves Earth” competition
will be announced September 15.

